
                                            Gautrain has confirmed the 61-year-old man was killed on Thursday afternoon.
                                         JOHANNESBURG - Police are investigating the death of a man who was hit by the Gautrain  near the Midrand depot. Gautrain has confirmed the 61-year-old man was killed on Thursday afternoon. Spokesperson Kasagee Nayager said: “At this stage, we can’t confirm if it was a suicide or suicide-related.”